cyphertite (1.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add root CA for cyphertite.com SSL verification
  * Implement easy/expert mode in config generation
  * Add cert autoretrieval based on curl
  * Include <ct_threads.h> not "ct_threads.h" as it is not in same dir
  * Remove use of a temporary pointer in ct_ssl_connect and fix a leak
  * Update install scripts to look for event_core
  * Enable threads when _REENTRANT is defined
  * No openat() on openbsd before 5.0
  * Consistently use ct_body_alloc_xml() with xmlsd_generate()
  * Fix several occurances of double semicolons at end of line
  * Fix an incorrect usage of e_free
  * Clog flags must be uint32_t, or CLOG_F_DBGENABLE sets the sign bit
  * Avoid using sizeof on a pointer with bzero
  * Free event globals based on allocation state
  * Update RPM package control spec for libevent2
  * Handle a few event_new allocation failures
  * Update to use libevent2 API
  * Abstract event loop break and cleanup logic
  * Turn on exude threads if both are on
  * Use better if condition checks for ENABLE_THREADS
  * Rework and cleanup thread handling
  * Consolidate common Makefile bits and cleanup
  * Move the ctutil linking logic into the cyphertite makefiles
  * Prompt user to overwrite existing cyphertite.conf
  * Fix overwrite of existing cypherite.conf file
  * Some FreeBSD package fixes were dropped on the initial commit
  * Add another var to struct fnode that will be needed in future
  * Move ct_populate_fnode and ct_normalize_path to a more appropriate place
  * Add current directory to inc path for extensions
  * Use include path for extension scaffolding
  * Secrets_upload -> upload_crypto_secrets spello
  * Fix a spello, spaces and some grammar
  * Ct_assl_ctx shouldn't be a common (global) variable
  * Use a SIMPLEQ instead of an SLIST for the ctfile_list
  * Scaffolding for extensions to cyphertite
  * Allow for XML commands, settings and ctcl commands from 3rd parties
  * Need to include inttypes.h for exude header
  * Split config path handling out into a seperate file
  * Other minor cleanup and bug fixes

 -- Conformal Systems <package-discuss@conformal.com>  Tue, 24 Apr 2012 17:36:31 -0500

cyphertite (1.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add pthreads support to provide a performance boost over previous
    releases of cyphertite
  * Fix extract error when extracting to another directory ie '-C'
  * Fix cull path problem where files were downloaded incorrectly
  * Update Copyrights for 2012
  * Packaging fixes for FreeBSD

 -- Conformal Systems <package-discuss@conformal.com>  Wed, 28 Mar 2012 17:06:15 -0500

cyphertite (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix major error in cull processing
  * Implement a major security enhancement on most systems by using
    openat(2) to securely walk directory trees instead of opening
    paths which could get renamed out from under the application
  * Cyphertite configuration file generation is now performed with
    'cyphertitectl config generate'
  * Crypto secrets file generation is now done during configuration file
    generation, or explicitly with 'cyphertitectl secrets generate', as
    opposed  to automatically generating it
  * Add ctctl secrets upload/download to store a user's secrets file 
    on the server
  * Change the cyphertitectl command to change the secrets password to
    'ctctl secrets passwd'
  * Allow specific debug levels to be disabled, eg '-Dall,-exude'
  * Fix error in cyphertite file browser related to rooted backups (-cP)
  * Other minor cleanup and bug fixes

 -- Conformal Systems <package-discuss@conformal.com>  Fri, 23 Mar 2012 11:51:40 -0500

